inal impedance: Z = sqrt(144.69) = 12.03 Ω.\n- Step 13: State the final conclusion: the total impedance of the circuit is Z = 12.03 Ω.\n\nEXPLANATION:\nTo solve this, Identify the given values from the question: resistance R = 12 Ω, inductance L = 0.2 H, capacitance C = 50 μF, and frequency f = 50 Hz. After computing, the result is 12.03 Ω.\n\nANSWER: 12.03 Ω"}]}
