itute the expression from Step 3 into the result from\n- Step 2: Z_L = 80 × 2 / 3= 160 / 3 ≈ 53.33 Ω\n\nEXPLANATION:\nTo solve this, Determine the source voltage (U) from the resonance condition. At the resonant frequency (f₁ = 75 Hz), the total impedance of the circuit is equal to the resistance R because the inductive and capacitive reactances cancel each other out (Z_L1 = Z_C1). U = I × R = 1 A × 60 Ω = 60 V. After computing, the result is 53.33 Ω.\n\nANSWER: 53.33 Ω"}]}
